# psd-pdf-to-markdown engine. PIN TO THE PRE-1.0 LINE ON PURPOSE: pymupdf4llm 1.x
# (>=1.28) pulls in onnxruntime + numpy + networkx + protobuf for ML layout
# analysis — a heavy native stack that both bloats the image and mirrors the
# matplotlib footprint that tripped AgentCore's overlay-mount snapshotter
# (2026-05-18). The pre-1.0 line (resolves to 0.3.4) depends only on PyMuPDF
# (one native .so, few files) + tabulate, and does no runtime model download.
# Even so, PyMuPDF is native — the
# image MUST be boot-tested in AgentCore before trusting this; if boot fails,
# drop back to a pure-Python engine (pdfplumber/pypdf).
